{
  "lessonId": 3,
  "exercises": [
    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-03-01",
      "stem": "计算 $a^6 \\div a^2$ 的结果是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$a^3$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$a^4$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$a^8$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$a^{12}$" }
      ],
      "answer": "B",
      "analysis": "$a^6 \\div a^2 = a^{6-2} = a^4$，同底数幂相除，指数相减。"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-03-02",
      "stem": "下列各式中，正确的是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$a^0 = 0$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$a^{-1} = -a$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$3^{-2} = \\frac{1}{9}$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$(-2)^{-3} = \\frac{1}{8}$" }
      ],
      "answer": "C",
      "analysis": "A 应为 $a^0 = 1$（$a \\neq 0$）；B 应为 $a^{-1} = \\frac{1}{a}$；C 正确：$3^{-2} = \\frac{1}{3^2} = \\frac{1}{9}$；D 应为 $(-2)^{-3} = \\frac{1}{(-2)^3} = -\\frac{1}{8}$。"
    },
    {
      "type": "choice",
      "id": "ex-03-03",
      "stem": "若 $2^x = 8$，则 $x$ 的值为（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$2$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$3$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$4$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$6$" }
      ],
      "answer": "B",
      "analysis": "$8 = 2^3$，所以 $2^x = 2^3$，得 $x = 3$。"
    },
    {
      "type": "true_false",
      "id": "ex-03-04",
      "stem": "$5^0 = 0$。",
      "answer": false,
      "analysis": "任何不等于零的数的零次幂都等于 $1$，即 $5^0 = 1$。"
    },
    {
      "type": "fill",
      "id": "ex-03-05",
      "segments": ["$2^{-3} = $___1___。"],
      "blanks": [
        { "index": 1, "answer": "$\\frac{1}{8}$" }
      ],
      "analysis": "$2^{-3} = \\frac{1}{2^3} = \\frac{1}{8}$。负整数指数幂等于正整数指数幂的倒数。"
    }
  ]
}